    "description": "Discipline: None\nSkill: Muscle\nType: Stance\nQi: 1\n\nYou inhale deeply and plant your feet firmly in the ground, thrusting out your hands. You channel your internal power to your fingers to protect against Attacks. When used normally you are very difficult to throw or move, giving opponents -1d10 to their Grapple or Throw attempts against you. However you cannot move more than 5 feet while in this stance. Cathartic: When used Cathartically this prevents Damage. You absorb one Wound against anyone whose Qi is lower than your own.",
